enhanced_by.reason: The lockedProductList method provides a list of available locked products, which is necessary to determine the validity of the projectId parameter in lockedSubscriptionPreview.
The simpleAccount method provides account-related information that might be necessary to validate the subscription preview request.

The lockedSubscriptionRecord method retrieves historical subscription records, which can be used to verify the correctness of the subscription preview by comparing the expected and actual subscription details.
The lockedPersonalLeftQuota method provides the remaining quota for locked subscriptions, which can be used to assert that the subscription preview does not exceed the available quota.
